WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.480 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:08.930 align:middle line:90%


00:00:08.930 --> 00:00:13.110 align:middle line:84%
>> It all started with a
worrying underhyped information

00:00:13.110 --> 00:00:13.910 align:middle line:90%
from Denmark.

00:00:13.910 --> 00:00:20.810 align:middle line:90%


00:00:20.810 --> 00:00:26.090 align:middle line:84%
Here, almost all breeding
animals are fed with GM soy.

00:00:26.090 --> 00:00:30.020 align:middle line:84%
For a few years, pig farming
has been facing a disease

00:00:30.020 --> 00:00:32.030 align:middle line:90%
with unknown causes.

00:00:32.030 --> 00:00:35.840 align:middle line:84%
Violent diarrhea,
often causing death.

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:38.990 align:middle line:84%
Danish farmers call
it the yellow death.

00:00:38.990 --> 00:00:45.370 align:middle line:90%


00:00:45.370 --> 00:00:47.420 align:middle line:90%
>> This is quite remarkable.

00:00:47.420 --> 00:00:49.900 align:middle line:84%
They have been in here for
five weeks and nobody died.

00:00:49.900 --> 00:00:50.950 align:middle line:90%
>> Nobody died.

00:00:50.950 --> 00:00:51.750 align:middle line:90%
>> Nobody died.

00:00:51.750 --> 00:00:52.930 align:middle line:90%
>> And it's unusual.

00:00:52.930 --> 00:00:54.380 align:middle line:90%
>> It's unusual just here.

00:00:54.380 --> 00:00:57.070 align:middle line:84%
But it could be
tomorrow, I get one.

00:00:57.070 --> 00:00:59.840 align:middle line:84%
I have some-- see
this diarrhea here.

00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:02.070 align:middle line:90%
There's a little bit here.

00:01:02.070 --> 00:01:03.760 align:middle line:84%
There's one pig
standing there with--

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:05.269 align:middle line:90%
on her legs.

00:01:05.269 --> 00:01:06.550 align:middle line:90%
That you need to watch.

00:01:06.550 --> 00:01:21.480 align:middle line:90%


00:01:21.480 --> 00:01:24.260 align:middle line:84%
>> Pedersen is a
breeding technician.

00:01:24.260 --> 00:01:26.750 align:middle line:84%
His animals' feed
is computer-managed

00:01:26.750 --> 00:01:28.520 align:middle line:90%
for each and every one of them.

00:01:28.520 --> 00:01:31.810 align:middle line:90%


00:01:31.810 --> 00:01:34.370 align:middle line:84%
Like all Danish
farmers, Pedersen

00:01:34.370 --> 00:01:38.920 align:middle line:84%
used GM soy flour
for a long time.

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:42.730 align:middle line:84%
>> I think the first bout
would have come in '96.

00:01:42.730 --> 00:01:44.680 align:middle line:84%
When we started,
it was not all GM.

00:01:44.680 --> 00:01:48.370 align:middle line:84%
Maybe, what, 20%
GM in the soy mix.

00:01:48.370 --> 00:01:52.190 align:middle line:84%
And then it got
gradually more and more.

00:01:52.190 --> 00:01:55.960 align:middle line:84%
And by 2001 you
would have had 90%.

00:01:55.960 --> 00:01:59.380 align:middle line:84%
>> Like all farmers, Peterson
had to face frequent diarrhea

00:01:59.380 --> 00:02:00.430 align:middle line:90%
outbursts.

00:02:00.430 --> 00:02:04.720 align:middle line:84%
One day, he decided to stop
feeding GM soy to his pigs.

00:02:04.720 --> 00:02:05.800 align:middle line:90%
>> Back to normal.

00:02:05.800 --> 00:02:07.175 align:middle line:84%
>> Just to see
how it would work.

00:02:07.175 --> 00:02:09.280 align:middle line:84%
>> Just to see
what was happening.

00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:13.720 align:middle line:84%
And then pay attention, if
some different thing came up.

00:02:13.720 --> 00:02:16.300 align:middle line:90%
Well, I didn't tell my herdsmen.

00:02:16.300 --> 00:02:19.240 align:middle line:84%
And two days after,
he'd come, my herdsman,

00:02:19.240 --> 00:02:21.264 align:middle line:90%
have you changed the food?

00:02:21.264 --> 00:02:22.640 align:middle line:90%
Said yeah.

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:23.840 align:middle line:90%
Is it bad?

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:24.790 align:middle line:90%
No, no.

00:02:24.790 --> 00:02:25.750 align:middle line:90%
Not this time.

00:02:25.750 --> 00:02:27.010 align:middle line:90%
And he said, look.

00:02:27.010 --> 00:02:28.540 align:middle line:90%
I have no diarrhea.

00:02:28.540 --> 00:02:30.250 align:middle line:90%
There's no diarrhea here.

00:02:30.250 --> 00:02:35.150 align:middle line:84%
And he has used 100
milliliter antibiotic--

00:02:35.150 --> 00:02:38.320 align:middle line:84%
to cure diarrhea that we
had massive problems with.

00:02:38.320 --> 00:02:40.840 align:middle line:90%
Up to 30% of piglets die.

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:41.980 align:middle line:90%
And it was really severe.

00:02:41.980 --> 00:02:45.010 align:middle line:90%


00:02:45.010 --> 00:02:47.710 align:middle line:84%
And the funny thing
is, and the good thing

00:02:47.710 --> 00:02:50.140 align:middle line:84%
is, we had three
years on non-GM.

00:02:50.140 --> 00:02:52.060 align:middle line:84%
We are not seeing
the sickness again.

00:02:52.060 --> 00:02:54.940 align:middle line:90%


00:02:54.940 --> 00:02:58.330 align:middle line:84%
>> By himself, Pedersen managed
to cast doubt in the kingdom

00:02:58.330 --> 00:02:59.370 align:middle line:90%
of Denmark.

00:02:59.370 --> 00:03:02.560 align:middle line:84%
What if something in
the transgenic soy

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:07.540 align:middle line:84%
was responsible for
these digestive diseases?

00:03:07.540 --> 00:03:11.680 align:middle line:84%
>> It was a very big mystery,
because I have grown--

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:14.590 align:middle line:84%
brought up cattle
all my life, so.

00:03:14.590 --> 00:03:20.540 align:middle line:84%
>> They were just giving up
like they just want to die.

00:03:20.540 --> 00:03:22.960 align:middle line:90%
I have a movie here.

00:03:22.960 --> 00:03:25.140 align:middle line:90%
So this black cow--

00:03:25.140 --> 00:03:28.200 align:middle line:84%
>> And those cows are
not alive anymore, right?

00:03:28.200 --> 00:03:29.200 align:middle line:90%
>> No.

00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:32.650 align:middle line:84%
>> I think we took these
pictures just before we put

00:03:32.650 --> 00:03:33.520 align:middle line:90%
them down.

00:03:33.520 --> 00:03:34.671 align:middle line:90%
You look this pic.

00:03:34.671 --> 00:03:36.144 align:middle line:90%
>> Pretty bad, huh.

00:03:36.144 --> 00:03:43.520 align:middle line:90%


00:03:43.520 --> 00:03:48.405 align:middle line:84%
>> I always linked this outbreak
of diarrhea in multiple herds

00:03:48.405 --> 00:03:55.860 align:middle line:84%
with a ship of soy that come
from one part of Argentina.

00:03:55.860 --> 00:03:58.830 align:middle line:84%
And then when that is
fed to a lot of farmers,

00:03:58.830 --> 00:04:01.222 align:middle line:84%
they all have diarrhea
in their herd.

00:04:01.222 --> 00:04:02.910 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:04:02.910 --> 00:04:05.280 align:middle line:84%
