>> They say it may be a
genetic problem but that it was

00:06:33.470 --> 00:06:34.790 align:middle line:90%
aggravated with fumigation.

00:06:34.790 --> 00:06:42.090 align:middle line:90%


00:06:42.090 --> 00:06:44.020 align:middle line:84%
>> The doctors told
you about herbicides?

00:06:44.020 --> 00:06:44.350 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:06:44.350 --> 00:06:45.440 align:middle line:90%
That's what they told me.

00:06:45.440 --> 00:06:55.690 align:middle line:90%


00:06:55.690 --> 00:06:58.300 align:middle line:84%
And in the village, there
are many deformed children.

00:06:58.300 --> 00:07:02.390 align:middle line:90%


00:07:02.390 --> 00:07:03.460 align:middle line:90%
People must know.

00:07:03.460 --> 00:07:11.290 align:middle line:90%


00:07:11.290 --> 00:07:14.490 align:middle line:84%
I feel bad because I wanted
the best for my daughter.

00:07:14.490 --> 00:07:19.600 align:middle line:90%


00:07:19.600 --> 00:07:21.290 align:middle line:90%
It's hard not to hate destiny.

00:07:21.290 --> 00:07:25.650 align:middle line:90%


00:07:25.650 --> 00:07:28.340 align:middle line:84%
I had really hard
times with her.

00:07:28.340 --> 00:07:31.380 align:middle line:90%


00:07:31.380 --> 00:07:33.690 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes, I even
felt like giving up.

00:07:33.690 --> 00:07:37.930 align:middle line:90%


00:07:37.930 --> 00:07:39.240 align:middle line:90%
I felt like hiding her.

00:07:39.240 --> 00:07:40.752 align:middle line:90%
But, no, I can't.

00:07:40.752 --> 00:07:49.220 align:middle line:90%


00:07:49.220 --> 00:07:53.560 align:middle line:84%
Until God decides her fate,
I have to go on and help her.

00:07:53.560 --> 00:08:02.070 align:middle line:90%


00:08:02.070 --> 00:08:05.410 align:middle line:84%
>> The villagers live in
the fear of a tractor.

00:08:05.410 --> 00:08:10.390 align:middle line:84%
It either spreads water or
Roundup, Monsanto's glyphosate.

00:08:10.390 --> 00:08:11.780 align:middle line:90%
They call it the poison.

00:08:11.780 --> 00:08:17.600 align:middle line:90%


00:08:17.600 --> 00:08:20.100 align:middle line:84%
>> When you wake up and hear
that tractor spraying the field

00:08:20.100 --> 00:08:26.930 align:middle line:84%
with its poison, nobody
knows what's happening.

00:08:26.930 --> 00:08:28.390 align:middle line:90%
I lock myself home with my kids.

00:08:28.390 --> 00:08:35.650 align:middle line:90%


00:08:35.650 --> 00:08:39.780 align:middle line:84%
>> Here's a tractor filling
up its tanks near the well.

00:08:39.780 --> 00:08:42.659 align:middle line:90%
Is it water or pesticides?

00:08:42.659 --> 00:08:45.720 align:middle line:84%
