the law is clear.

00:08:45.720 --> 00:08:49.230 align:middle line:84%
Spreading is prohibited
within a 1.5 kilometer

00:08:49.230 --> 00:08:50.295 align:middle line:90%
distance from houses.

00:08:50.295 --> 00:09:12.316 align:middle line:90%


00:09:12.316 --> 00:09:14.820 align:middle line:90%
>> They're gone.

00:09:14.820 --> 00:09:17.370 align:middle line:90%
>> They can't be far.

00:09:17.370 --> 00:09:19.176 align:middle line:90%
>> They realized you were here.

00:09:19.176 --> 00:09:24.940 align:middle line:90%


00:09:24.940 --> 00:09:28.280 align:middle line:84%
>> The tractor came
from this GM soy field.

00:09:28.280 --> 00:09:29.860 align:middle line:90%
The field is guarded.

00:09:29.860 --> 00:09:31.570 align:middle line:90%
The situation is tense.

00:09:31.570 --> 00:09:35.495 align:middle line:84%
