with a hidden camera.

00:09:35.495 --> 00:09:36.330 align:middle line:90%
>> Hello, sir.

00:09:36.330 --> 00:09:38.370 align:middle line:90%
We are French journalists.

00:09:38.370 --> 00:09:41.350 align:middle line:90%
>> What do you want?

00:09:41.350 --> 00:09:45.753 align:middle line:84%
>> We are working on the soy
that's being produced here.

00:09:45.753 --> 00:09:47.420 align:middle line:84%
