France are eating it.

00:09:47.420 --> 00:09:54.480 align:middle line:90%


00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:55.280 align:middle line:90%
>> Go ahead.

00:09:55.280 --> 00:09:56.130 align:middle line:90%
Look around.

00:09:56.130 --> 00:09:56.930 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:09:56.930 --> 00:10:01.080 align:middle line:90%


00:10:01.080 --> 00:10:06.525 align:middle line:84%
>> I don't know what you're
looking for, but go ahead.

00:10:06.525 --> 00:10:09.990 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:10:09.990 --> 00:10:12.750 align:middle line:84%
>> The village is
200 meters away.

00:10:12.750 --> 00:10:15.530 align:middle line:90%
