00:10:15.530 --> 00:10:20.420 align:middle line:84%
Hidden in soy plants, there's
half a dozen chemical cans,

00:10:20.420 --> 00:10:24.120 align:middle line:84%
and herbicide glyphosate,
without which GM soy cannot

00:10:24.120 --> 00:10:24.920 align:middle line:90%
exist.

00:10:24.920 --> 00:10:30.920 align:middle line:90%


00:10:30.920 --> 00:10:33.250 align:middle line:90%
