at the same time.

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:44.240 align:middle line:90%
Weeds can suffocate soy.

00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:47.030 align:middle line:84%
This is when
glyphosate comes in.

00:10:47.030 --> 00:10:51.920 align:middle line:84%
