everything but GM soy.

00:10:51.920 --> 00:10:53.000 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:10:53.000 --> 00:10:55.740 align:middle line:84%
Because the soy has
been modified to resist.

00:10:55.740 --> 00:11:00.275 align:middle line:90%
It's become herbicide-proofed.

00:11:00.275 --> 00:11:03.080 align:middle line:84%
>> There are lots of
