>> Yes.

00:11:04.200 --> 00:11:05.470 align:middle line:90%
>> In Chaco, lots of weeds.

00:11:05.470 --> 00:11:08.305 align:middle line:90%


00:11:08.305 --> 00:11:10.020 align:middle line:90%
>> How do you solve the problem?

00:11:10.020 --> 00:11:13.260 align:middle line:90%


00:11:13.260 --> 00:11:15.220 align:middle line:90%
>> With poison.

00:11:15.220 --> 00:11:17.860 align:middle line:84%
We use Roundup to
get rid of the weeds.

00:11:17.860 --> 00:11:22.958 align:middle line:90%


