>> You can no longer
eat their eggs.

00:11:46.060 --> 00:11:49.168 align:middle line:90%


00:11:49.168 --> 00:11:50.210 align:middle line:90%
>> This field is treated?

00:11:50.210 --> 00:11:51.418 align:middle line:90%
Until the village over there?

