They are scum.

00:12:14.840 --> 00:12:15.650 align:middle line:90%
It's a slum.

00:12:15.650 --> 00:12:21.940 align:middle line:90%


00:12:21.940 --> 00:12:25.530 align:middle line:84%
>> Last year, we met up with
the nearby soy producers,

00:12:25.530 --> 00:12:28.670 align:middle line:84%
and the people in
charge of fumigation.

00:12:28.670 --> 00:12:31.435 align:middle line:90%
We were several villages.

00:12:31.435 --> 00:12:35.205 align:middle line:84%
I went to the meeting because
of my daughter's condition.

