00:16:44.610 --> 00:16:46.497 align:middle line:84%
It's true, there are
more than before.

00:16:46.497 --> 00:16:48.330 align:middle line:84%
But maybe it's because
they are less hidden.

00:16:48.330 --> 00:17:04.640 align:middle line:90%


00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:11.295 align:middle line:84%
>> There are twice as many
specialized institutions,

00:17:11.295 --> 00:17:13.420 align:middle line:84%
which have opened secondary
centers in many smaller

00:17:13.420 --> 00:17:14.220 align:middle line:90%
villages.

00:17:14.220 --> 00:17:21.359 align:middle line:90%


00:17:21.359 --> 00:17:24.240 align:middle line:84%
>> For two years, images of
this strange deformed children

00:17:24.240 --> 00:17:26.819 align:middle line:84%
epidemic have started to
