pigs in the past,

00:17:43.870 --> 00:17:47.580 align:middle line:84%
when we had one with two
heads, or elephant man heads,

00:17:47.580 --> 00:17:51.340 align:middle line:90%
or a girl and a boy, same time.

00:17:51.340 --> 00:17:54.410 align:middle line:84%
I, like any other farmer, had
got more or less accustomed

00:17:54.410 --> 00:17:55.210 align:middle line:90%
to that.

00:17:55.210 --> 00:17:57.800 align:middle line:90%
We had deformities.

00:17:57.800 --> 00:18:00.700 align:middle line:90%
So it was not new to me.

00:18:00.700 --> 00:18:02.560 align:middle line:90%
Back legs not much use.

00:18:02.560 --> 00:18:05.120 align:middle line:90%


00:18:05.120 --> 00:18:07.840 align:middle line:84%
It's like, you'd think he
should have longer legs.

00:18:07.840 --> 00:18:10.236 align:middle line:84%
He can't really make
them reach the floor.

00:18:10.236 --> 00:18:13.200 align:middle line:90%


00:18:13.200 --> 00:18:16.470 align:middle line:84%
When this down in
Argentina, when

00:18:16.470 --> 00:18:19.800 align:middle line:84%
they had these
deformed children,

00:18:19.800 --> 00:18:21.070 align:middle line:90%
is that the same deformity?

