It looks like the same
I had with my pigs.

00:18:24.300 --> 00:18:27.870 align:middle line:84%
>> In Argentina, the government
is supporting transgenic

00:18:27.870 --> 00:18:29.420 align:middle line:90%
agriculture.

00:18:29.420 --> 00:18:33.660 align:middle line:84%
It denied the existence of
this epidemic for a long time.

00:18:33.660 --> 00:18:37.300 align:middle line:84%
Today, denial is no
longer an option.

00:18:37.300 --> 00:18:39.450 align:middle line:84%
But at the Ministry for
Science, they rather

00:18:39.450 --> 00:18:41.714 align:middle line:90%
mention an accident.

00:18:41.714 --> 00:18:42.514 align:middle line:90%
>> It's true.

00:18:42.514 --> 00:18:44.639 align:middle line:84%
There's a quite clear
correlation with the progress

00:18:44.639 --> 00:18:47.180 align:middle line:90%
of the agricultural border.

00:18:47.180 --> 00:18:47.980 align:middle line:90%
It's undeniable.

00:18:47.980 --> 00:18:51.100 align:middle line:84%
And that may be linked
to chemical use.

00:18:51.100 --> 00:18:55.980 align:middle line:84%
We don't know how they use it,
they're not cautious enough.

00:18:55.980 --> 00:18:58.616 align:middle line:90%
The population is too exposed.

00:18:58.616 --> 00:19:01.950 align:middle line:84%
And also, we don't know what
combinations of chemicals

00:19:01.950 --> 00:19:04.680 align:middle line:90%
are being used.

00:19:04.680 --> 00:19:07.410 align:middle line:90%
>> Combinations of chemicals.

00:19:07.410 --> 00:19:09.940 align:middle line:90%
We never heard of that before.

00:19:09.940 --> 00:19:13.030 align:middle line:84%
Transgenic firms have
always guaranteed

00:19:13.030 --> 00:19:14.530 align:middle line:84%
that you didn't
need anything else

00:19:14.530 --> 00:19:18.180 align:middle line:84%
but glyphosate to
weed the fields.

00:19:18.180 --> 00:19:20.970 align:middle line:84%
As confessed by the
Ministry for Science,

00:19:20.970 --> 00:19:25.530 align:middle line:84%
farmers are adding unknown
substances out of any control.

00:19:25.530 --> 00:19:26.970 align:middle line:90%
What are those chemicals?

00:19:26.970 --> 00:19:32.350 align:middle line:90%


00:19:32.350 --> 00:19:35.710 align:middle line:84%
Near a cornfield, there's
a spreading tractor.

00:19:35.710 --> 00:19:37.210 align:middle line:90%
No one around.

00:19:37.210 --> 00:19:39.640 align:middle line:84%
On the tractor,
we find glyphosate

00:19:39.640 --> 00:19:41.680 align:middle line:90%
produced by Monsanto.

00:19:41.680 --> 00:19:43.270 align:middle line:90%
Nothing surprising.

00:19:43.270 --> 00:19:47.500 align:middle line:84%
But we also find two
other chemicals, atrazine,

00:19:47.500 --> 00:19:49.900 align:middle line:90%
which is forbidden in Europe.

00:19:49.900 --> 00:19:54.040 align:middle line:84%
According to an American study,
atrazine turns male frogs

00:19:54.040 --> 00:19:56.470 align:middle line:90%
into female frogs.

00:19:56.470 --> 00:20:02.110 align:middle line:84%
There's also 2.4-D, one of the
two components of Agent Orange,

00:20:02.110 --> 00:20:04.180 align:middle line:90%
a military herbicide.

00:20:04.180 --> 00:20:07.720 align:middle line:84%
To find enemies hidden in the
forest during the Vietnam War,

00:20:07.720 --> 00:20:10.900 align:middle line:84%
the American army had
been weeding the forests.

00:20:10.900 --> 00:20:14.650 align:middle line:84%
Very efficient, except for the
people who were underneath.

00:20:14.650 --> 00:20:16.600 align:middle line:84%
Thousands of deformed
children were

00:20:16.600 --> 00:20:18.025 align:middle line:90%
born in the following years.

00:20:18.025 --> 00:20:21.390 align:middle line:90%


00:20:21.390 --> 00:20:25.880 align:middle line:84%
Today, American health
authorities assert that 2.4-D

00:20:25.880 --> 00:20:29.360 align:middle line:84%
was the least dangerous
component of Agent Orange.

00:20:29.360 --> 00:20:33.720 align:middle line:84%
Dow Chemical is selling
it all across Argentina.

00:20:33.720 --> 00:20:35.670 align:middle line:90%
These products are toxic.

00:20:35.670 --> 00:20:38.070 align:middle line:90%
They seep through subsoil water.

00:20:38.070 --> 00:20:40.230 align:middle line:84%
The transgenic
promise was a world

00:20:40.230 --> 00:20:42.180 align:middle line:90%
with less and less chemicals.

00:20:42.180 --> 00:20:44.740 align:middle line:84%
What's happening is
the very opposite.

00:20:44.740 --> 00:20:49.640 align:middle line:90%


00:20:49.640 --> 00:20:51.170 align:middle line:90%
What's going on?

00:20:51.170 --> 00:20:54.140 align:middle line:84%
Governmental agronomists
encouraged farmers

00:20:54.140 --> 00:20:56.870 align:middle line:90%
to massively shift to GM crops.

00:20:56.870 --> 00:20:59.450 align:middle line:84%
And now they are
facing mutant enemies.

00:20:59.450 --> 00:21:04.025 align:middle line:90%


00:21:04.025 --> 00:21:07.380 align:middle line:84%
>> All that's green
there is weeds?

00:21:07.380 --> 00:21:09.030 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, pretty much.

00:21:09.030 --> 00:21:10.455 align:middle line:90%
>> What happened?

00:21:10.455 --> 00:21:12.790 align:middle line:84%
By sewing 30 million
hectares of GM soy,

00:21:12.790 --> 00:21:19.676 align:middle line:84%
resistant to glyphosate, with
3 or 4 applications a year,

00:21:19.676 --> 00:21:22.176 align:middle line:84%
today, weeds that are resistant
to glyphosate have appeared.

00:21:22.176 --> 00:21:25.090 align:middle line:90%


00:21:25.090 --> 00:21:27.283 align:middle line:84%
>> So you have to constantly
increase the quantity?

00:21:27.283 --> 00:21:29.380 align:middle line:90%
>> Of course.

00:21:29.380 --> 00:21:31.510 align:middle line:84%
What we do is we mix
different active substances

00:21:31.510 --> 00:21:33.680 align:middle line:84%
to prevent weeds from
adapting to herbicides.

00:21:33.680 --> 00:21:37.445 align:middle line:90%


00:21:37.445 --> 00:21:39.570 align:middle line:84%
By mixing ingredients, we
prevent their resistance.

00:21:39.570 --> 00:21:42.510 align:middle line:90%


00:21:42.510 --> 00:21:43.670 align:middle line:90%
>> You're fixing cocktails.

00:21:43.670 --> 00:21:45.750 align:middle line:90%
>> Exactly.

00:21:45.750 --> 00:21:49.540 align:middle line:84%
>> It seems transgenic
firms got it all wrong.

00:21:49.540 --> 00:21:51.780 align:middle line:84%
They promised ever
less chemicals.

00:21:51.780 --> 00:21:54.690 align:middle line:90%
What happens is the contrary.

00:21:54.690 --> 00:21:58.200 align:middle line:84%
Glyphosate is no longer
enough to control weeds.

00:21:58.200 --> 00:22:03.360 align:middle line:84%
Now, three, four, or five other
chemicals need to be added.

00:22:03.360 --> 00:22:05.730 align:middle line:84%
Next generation seeds
will be designed

00:22:05.730 --> 00:22:08.340 align:middle line:84%
to resist even more
toxic combinations.

00:22:08.340 --> 00:22:09.680 align:middle line:90%
That wasn't quite the plan.

00:22:09.680 --> 00:22:14.840 align:middle line:90%


