it was supposed to.

00:23:11.190 --> 00:23:13.620 align:middle line:90%
Maybe they feel responsible.

00:23:13.620 --> 00:23:16.890 align:middle line:84%
Argentinean farmers
relied on them.

00:23:16.890 --> 00:23:19.726 align:middle line:84%
Themselves, they put
their trust in Monsanto.

00:23:19.726 --> 00:23:22.100 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:23:22.100 --> 00:23:32.940 align:middle line:90%


00:23:32.940 --> 00:23:36.030 align:middle line:84%
>> Monsanto declined
answering our questions,

00:23:36.030 --> 00:23:40.050 align:middle line:84%
neither in front of a
camera nor in writing.

00:23:40.050 --> 00:23:43.560 align:middle line:84%
However, every
night, Argentinean TV

00:23:43.560 --> 00:23:47.520 align:middle line:84%
