Monsanto ads.

00:23:47.520 --> 00:23:50.760 align:middle line:84%
They guarantee that roundup,
their glyphosate-based

00:23:50.760 --> 00:23:52.530 align:middle line:90%
herbicide, is very efficient.

00:23:52.530 --> 00:23:55.080 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:23:55.080 --> 00:23:58.440 align:middle line:90%


00:23:58.440 --> 00:24:00.870 align:middle line:84%
>> Nothing proves that
transgenic agriculture is

00:24:00.870 --> 00:24:03.990 align:middle line:84%
