tried to figure it out.

00:24:08.880 --> 00:24:11.520 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:24:11.520 --> 00:24:52.050 align:middle line:90%


00:24:52.050 --> 00:24:55.800 align:middle line:84%
>> The Argentinean ministry for
health hasn't done anything.

00:24:55.800 --> 00:24:59.250 align:middle line:84%
