surrounding villages.

00:25:26.660 --> 00:25:30.620 align:middle line:84%
They sleep in gym facilities and
interview the whole population

00:25:30.620 --> 00:25:32.030 align:middle line:90%
on their medical conditions.

00:25:32.030 --> 00:25:39.810 align:middle line:90%


00:25:39.810 --> 00:26:20.060 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:26:20.060 --> 00:26:24.170 align:middle line:84%
>> Cancer rates
